{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":3,"day":4}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"《赤道战鼓》序幕朗诵词","authors":[],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“战斗吧！刚果！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烈日如火的赤道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成长着英雄的黑色儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大西洋漫卷的风暴里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳动着黑非洲的心脏。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果啊，灾难深重的刚果！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十多年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你带着满身的创伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖着镣铐、枷锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过了漫长痛苦的岁月。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十多年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千万黑人兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千七百万被屠杀、贩卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难深重的刚果啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走过了漫长痛苦的岁月！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋上风雷滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的最强音在黑非洲的上空响彻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起来，饥寒交迫的奴隶！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起来，不愿作奴隶的人们！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独立不能乞求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要自由就要拿起武器战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要解放你乌黑的身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要用你自己乌黑的双手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来吧！战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先进的大陆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉醒的非洲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤道战鼓擂动了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果啊！战斗！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}